Package App.LicenseClient

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActKey
    ActKey Class helps in starting an activation flow which includes: 1.
    Apple
    This class is the main runner class which runs the whole flow of the licensing module.
    Base
    Base class This class contains all the reusable methods which can come handy in many classes for easy code flow, and hence this class will be extended to most classes as parent class.
    CheckFlagStat
    CheckFlagStat class was designed to help check the status of all flags at any instance of the functional flow to trigger actions based on the flag status
    ComputerIdentifier
    ComputerIdentifier class is the integration class which utilizes the external open API which helps getting all required information of the machine and creating the Machine ID in the required format
    MainRunner  
    RequestLic
    This class helps in creating a request for license purchase for which we need to create Machine specific files and the Public /Private Keys which will be used to sign and verify Digital Signature flow
    SymEncPM
    SymEnc Class is the first level of symmetric encryption technique implemented within the module for encrypting the machineID data generated
    Verifications
    Verifications class helps in verifying all checks before every time the application is started to ensure and start the correct version of the application (demo or full mode)
